  "body": "### Meeting Info\r\n\r\n* [August 20, 2021, 14:00 UTC](https://savvytime.com/converter/utc-to-germany-berlin-united-kingdom-london-ny-new-york-city-ca-san-francisco-china-shanghai-japan-tokyo-australia-sydney/aug-20-2021/2pm)\r\n* Duration: 90 minutes\r\n* Youtube Stream: https://youtu.be/rlIgpf2V4ks\r\n* Zoom: To be shared on #allcoredevs Discord server shortly before the call \r\n\r\n### Agenda\r\n\r\n* Merge updates https://github.com/ethereum/pm/issues/361 \r\n    * [Consensus API design space](https://hackmd.io/@n0ble/consensus_api_design_space)\r\n* London Retrospective ([link](https://hackmd.io/@timbeiko/london-retro))\r\n* Limiting account nonce: EIP 2681 vs. 3338 see comments [1](https://github.com/ethereum/pm/issues/370#issuecomment-896916769), [2](https://github.com/ethereum/pm/issues/370#issuecomment-896919951)\r\n* [EIP-1352](https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-1352), see [comment](https://github.com/ethereum/pm/issues/370#issuecomment-902040752)\r\n* eth/65 deprecation https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/pull/23120 \r\n* [EIP-3607](https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-3607), https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/pull/23303 \r\n* Announcements: \r\n     * Geth hotfix v1.10.8 \r\n     * JSON RPC spec reviews https://github.com/ethereum/execution-apis/issues/56\r\n     * Repository / discord renaming from eth1/eth2 to execution/consensus, [link](https://notes.ethereum.org/@timbeiko/great-renaming)\r\n     * https://github.com/ethereum/pm/issues/377",
